const initialState = {
  gloria: [

    { id: 'assets/images/gloria_sofa/10.jpeg' },
    { id: 'assets/images/gloria_sofa/11.jpeg' },
    { id: 'assets/images/gloria_sofa/12.jpeg' },
  ],
  afilli: [
    { id: 'assets/images/wood_sofa_team_afilli/A48A2588.jpeg' },
    { id: 'assets/images/wood_sofa_team_afilli/A48A2554.jpeg' },

    { id: 'assets/images/wood_sofa_team_han_tekstil/A48A9877.jpg' },
    { id: 'assets/images/wood_sofa_team_han_tekstil/A48A9874.jpg' },
    { id: 'assets/images/wood_sofa_team_afilli/A48A2557.jpeg' },
    { id: 'assets/images/wood_sofa_team_afilli/A48A2574.jpeg' },
    { id: 'assets/images/wood_sofa_team_afilli/A48A2574.jpeg' },
  ],
  han: [
    { id: 'assets/images/wood_sofa_team_han_tekstil/A48A9884.jpg' },
    { id: 'assets/images/wood_sofa_team_han_tekstil/A48A9887.jpg' },
    { id: 'assets/images/wood_sofa_team_han_tekstil/A48A9880.jpg' },
    { id: 'assets/images/wood_sofa_team_han_tekstil/A48A9892.jpg' },

    { id: 'assets/images/wood_sofa_team_han_tekstil/A48A9897.jpg' },
  ],
  dortmund: [
    { id: "assets/images/dortmund/1.jpeg" },
    { id: "assets/images/dortmund/2.jpeg" },
    { id: "assets/images/dortmund/3.jpeg" },
    { id: "assets/images/dortmund/4.jpeg" },

    { id: "assets/images/dortmund/6.jpeg" },

    { id: "assets/images/dortmund/9.jpeg" },
  ],
  media: [

    { id: "assets/images/media/3.jpg" },
    { id: "assets/images/media/1.jpg" },
    { id: "assets/images/media/4.jpg" },
    { id: "assets/images/media/6.jpg" },
    { id: "assets/images/media/2.jpg" },
    { id: "assets/images/media/5.jpg" },
  ],
  countt: 0,
  header: 0,
  countState: null,
  countH: false,
}
const userManagament = createSlice({
  name: "userManagament",
  initialState,
  reducers: {
    countH: (state, action) => {
      state.countt = action.payload
      state.countG = false
      state.countD = false
      state.countW = false
      state.countH = true
    },
    countD: (state, action) => {
      state.countt = action.payload
      state.countH = false
      state.countW = false
      state.countG = false
      state.countD = true
    },
    countW: (state, action) => {
      state.countt = action.payload
      state.countD = null
      state.countH = null
      state.countG = null
      state.countW = true
    },
    countG: (state, action) => {
      state.countt = action.payload
      state.countD = null
      state.countH = null
      state.countW = null
      state.countG = true
    },
    countM: (state, action) => {
      state.countt = action.payload
      state.countG = null
      state.countD = null
      state.countH = null
      state.countW = null
      state.countM = true
    },
    headers: (state, action) => {
      state.header = action.payload
    },
  }
})

export const { countD, countH, countW, countG, countM, headers } = userManagament.actions;
export default userManagament.reducer
